{#
  Partner Tour Section Component (Story 2.6)

  Displays "Need Hands-On Guidance?" section on scenario detail pages.
  Provides alternative path for organisations preferring guided evaluation.

  Features (AC-2.6.1):
    - "Need Hands-On Guidance?" heading
    - "Schedule a Partner Tour" button
    - Brief explanation of partner-led evaluation sessions
    - Links to dedicated partner tour request form/page

  Expects scenarioData context from parent template.
#}

{% if scenarioData %}
<div class="ndx-partner-tour-section" id="partner-tour">
  <hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--l govuk-section-break--visible">

  <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Need hands-on guidance?</h2>

  <div class="govuk-grid-row">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
      <p class="govuk-body-l">
        Not ready to deploy yourself? Our implementation partners can guide your team through a live evaluation session.
      </p>

      <p class="govuk-body">
        During a <strong>30-60 minute guided tour</strong>, a vetted implementation partner will:
      </p>

      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>Walk through the {{ scenarioData.name }} scenario with your team</li>
        <li>Answer technical and business questions in real-time</li>
        <li>Help you understand how this applies to your organisation's needs</li>
        <li>Provide guidance on next steps and procurement options</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="govuk-body">
        <strong>No AWS account required</strong> - the partner handles the deployment while you observe and learn.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
      <div class="ndx-partner-tour-section__cta">
        <a href="/partner-tour/?scenario={{ scenarioData.id }}"
           class="govuk-button govuk-button--secondary ndx-partner-tour-section__button"
           data-module="govuk-button">
          Schedule a partner tour
        </a>

        <p class="govuk-body-s govuk-!-margin-top-2">
          Free of charge. No commitment required.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {# Additional info in details component #}
  <details class="govuk-details govuk-!-margin-top-4" data-module="govuk-details">
    <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
      <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">
        About our implementation partners
      </span>
    </summary>
    <div class="govuk-details__text">
      <p>Our implementation partners are:</p>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li><strong>Vetted by AWS</strong> - accredited AWS Partners with local government experience</li>
        <li><strong>Public sector specialists</strong> - experienced in local government requirements and procurement</li>
        <li><strong>G-Cloud listed</strong> - available through existing public sector frameworks</li>
        <li><strong>Regional coverage</strong> - partners available across the UK</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="govuk-link">Contact us</a> if you'd like to learn more about our partner network.
      </p>
    </div>
  </details>
</div>
{% endif %}
